Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:06.52,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kessoku Band managed to succeed \Nin its first full four-member concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:09.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And so, our summer came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:10.82,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.3\fs30\fnArial Black\c&H36160B&\pos(315.556,83.111)}August
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:10.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,a middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:15.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We do have \Nsome break left, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:23.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Until my summer break comes to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:26.36,DefaultTop,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What lovely weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:27.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to spend every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,enjoying it to its fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.67,DefaultTop,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Another fulfilling day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:40.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:43.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer break, but I'm not \Ndoing a single thing differently!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:43.89,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(29,3157,\fscx110.02\fscy110.02)\blur0.3\fs12\fnArial Black\c&H36160B&\fay-0.2\move(321.5,136.5,320.88,130.55,29,3157)}August
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:48.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, playing guitar is fun and all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking Kessoku Band \Nmight hang out together,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:54.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,so I've cleared my schedule \Nof everything but work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:57.61,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's usually \Nclear regardless, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:02.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But {\i0}keeping{\i1} it clear\Nhas a totally different feel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:07.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Still, even at work, nobody \Nso much as suggests hanging out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.59,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan! See you at work again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:14.92,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The members of a band usually \Nhang out, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess when we're all \Navailable, we should be practicing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.61,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Still, just for once, I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.19,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs9\c&H606060&\3c&HFDFFFD&\pos(322.5,55)}Kessoku Band
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.19,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\bord2\fs9\c&H606060&\3c&HFDFFFD&\pos(250.5,109.5)}Can anyone take my shift\N tomorrow? I've got stuff to do ^^;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.19,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs9\c&H606060&\3c&HFDFFFD&\pos(274,139.5)}I can take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.19,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\bord0.8\fs13\c&H322D2E&\3c&HF6EFF3&\pos(294,285.5)}GRATITUDE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:28.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always be passive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:32.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But if I bring it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:36.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll have to pick \Nthe place and time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:42.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of a plan \Nthat'll satisfy everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.75,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs9\c&H5F6667&\pos(320.5,206.5)}Nijika
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.75,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I just have to work up the courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.75,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with Nijika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.75,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(24,1984,\fscx108.46\fscy108.46)\fs18\fax0.03\c&H4D504E&\b0\frz6.981\move(327.31,91.63,328.29,84.13,24,1984)}Nijika
