Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.08,DefaultItalics,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It's a bit late to call now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:57.93,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan! Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:01.97,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, there's a lot of summer break left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:05.76,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure one of them will make \Nthe offer sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:06.98,Default,Kita/Kita's Friend A,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:15.82,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(984,602)\fs18\b0\bord1.5\c&HE09041&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(171.5,73.5)}What is the general theory of relativity?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.26,DefaultItalics,Man N,0000,0000,0000,,The general theory of relativity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:15.82,DefaultItalics,Man N,0000,0000,0000,,states that the passage of time slows \Nin the presence of a powerful gravity well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:15.82,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,602)\fs18\b0\bord1.5\c&H4251DE&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(302,97)}Time slows due to curvature of spacetime caused by a powerful gravity well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:22.28,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\bord1.5\c&H181C1B&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(434,319)}Artist's impression of a black hole drawing in matter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:20.20,DefaultItalicsTop,Man N,0000,0000,0000,,The black holes theorized \Nto exist throughout space
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:25.00,DefaultItalicsTop,Man N,0000,0000,0000,,are believed to be the end state \Nof the life cycle of massive stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:28.46,DefaultItalics,Man N,0000,0000,0000,,Their extreme density and \Nhigh gravitational potential
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:33.25,DefaultItalics,Man N,0000,0000,0000,,mean that not only matter, but even light, \Nbecomes trapped forever in their pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.92,DefaultItalics,Man N,0000,0000,0000,,The gravitational field causes time to slow \Nso much that it nearly stops...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.92,DefaultTop,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan! I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.55,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd air out the futons \Nwhile the weather's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.92,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie around all day, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.72,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be back at school soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:48.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm in a black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:53.02,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H33&\an8\bord0\blur0.3\p1\c&HF5FBF8&\pos(574,14.5)\fscx100\fscy131}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
