Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.86,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H4B0CCA&\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\pos(426,253)}#09 Enoshima Escar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan? Acting strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.64,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.45,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She's been staring out into space, \Nand she's barely talked in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.53,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like typical Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you can't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:39.92,Flashback,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Astaxanthin. Canthaxanthin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:40.65,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,...be exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.55,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed on the verge \Nof tears for a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.97,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,but then she spontaneously \Nstarted dancing the samba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.13,Flashback,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Tortilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.47,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.22,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Typical Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.48,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It is {\i1}not{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.73,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.94,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get Bocchi-chan to knock it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.90,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:08.90,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,She's been making cicada graves \Nin front of the club all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.32,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.87,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What's got her freaking out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because today's \Nthe last day of summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.98,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell. Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.99,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna go back to school either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:18.00,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Say, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:21.76,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Have you actually taken her out \Nanywhere this summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:27.34,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,One time, while you were working, I asked \Nwhat she was doing with her time off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:31.56,Flashback,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan. What are you doing with \Nyour break when you're not working?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:37.35,Flashback,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I... My little sister asked me \Nto teach her guitar, so I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.20,Flashback,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.80,Flashback,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:44.53,Flashback,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Today I asked my sister \Nto teach me to play guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:50.24,Flashback,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was awesome how my sister \Nstayed inside practicing, day after day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:55.41,Flashback,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,I have too many things to do and too many \Nfriends to play with over summer break,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.59,Flashback,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't stay home practicing \Nevery day like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.50,Flashback,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think it's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:06.82,Flashback,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Her words sent me into a spiral, and\N I ended up not getting out of bed for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:07.95,Flashback,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.50,Flashback,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I cleared my schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:13.10,Flashback,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not because I have nothing to do! \NI cleared it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.56,Flashback,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:15.84,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,She said all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:20.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to invite her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,My schedule's packed every day I'm not here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.28,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought she'd be uncomfortable \Naround people she doesn't know, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.04,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Ijichi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:35.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, when we're not practicing, I'm \Ncleaning up at home or working here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.66,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryo-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.17,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you two had invited her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.25,Default,Nijika/Ryo/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody invited Bocchi-chan out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.68,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You guys need to change your band name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.26,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gotoh-san! You want to hang out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:57.22,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Docosahexaenoic acid. Eicosapentaenoic acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.22,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:07:01.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's all go to the \Nbeach together, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We could hit up Enoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:05.65,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea! It's a straight shot \Nfrom Shimo-Kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.26,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.88,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What-about-our-practice-then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.07,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she talking like a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.81,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We can practice any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we have our next \Nconcert scheduled, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.68,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use our last day of summer break \Nto make memories together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:21.75,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.18,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.50,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the beach together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.69,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But it might be too late to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:31.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... no point in going to \Nthe beach if you can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.62,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,B-But there's still the beach shacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat shirasu-don!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And we can gaze at the ocean from the sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean... Sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:42.46,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,See? Doesn't that sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.66,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.76,Default,Guitar Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.10,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,The end of summer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.59,Default,Guitar Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come again next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.78,Default,Guitar Man/Guitar Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Tropical love forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.00,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Tropical love...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:19.92,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:20.92,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I think I made it worse somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's take her out while she's docile!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:29.66,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.07,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, you carry Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:35.59,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's get going to Enoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.54,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.79,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san! We'll be making \Nthose summer memories soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang in there a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.99,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Scary... Tropical...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:56.53,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a black hole... at the \Nfar reaches of the galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She must really hate school \Nto be acting this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.51,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Is your school super strict?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.92,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Too far for the sunshine \Nof summer to reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:02.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd say it's on the liberal side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:02.42,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Trapped by the powerful gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.64,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And the culture festivals are lots of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:09.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Our school's pretty strict,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and the culture festivals are super uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's mostly science project \Nposters and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:18.70,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H22&\an7\bord0\blur1\p1\c&HB2E6FB&\fscx211\fscy88\pos(39,15)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.69,0:09:18.70,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fnTimes New Roman\c&H130E76&\pos(145,20)}An Observation on the \NLifecycle of the Honeybee\N{\fs12}Phylum: Arthropoda  Class: Insecta  \NOrder: Hymenoptera  Family: Apidae  \NGenus: Apis  Scientific Name: Apis
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:18.70,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H22&\an7\bord0\blur1\p1\c&HB2E6FB&\fscx286\fscy85\pos(314,15)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.69,0:09:18.70,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fnTimes New Roman\c&H130E76&\pos(456,18)}An Investigation into the Weight of\N Ragworms Based on Environment \N{\fs12}Phylum: Annelida  Class: Polychaeta\N  Order: Phyllodocida  Family: Nereididae \NGenus: Hediste  Scientific Name: Hediste
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:15.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:18.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Shimo-Kitazawa High \Nis a prep school, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.20,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You two must be really smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty average, myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.93,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And Ryo is... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:26.77,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.47,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You bombed your last round of tests, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.03,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:30.63,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She picked the school for \Nthe same reason I did:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,because it was close to home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:35.99,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:40.35,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But then how did you pass the entrance exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.18,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo's a cram-the-night-before type.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She worked really hard right before the exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.19,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently forgot it all after.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:51.60,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,When I study too hard, \NI forget how to play bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:56.09,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Ryo-senpai isn't \Nmysterious and thoughtful at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:02.25,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,No! Her brain is so small you can hear it \Nrattling around in her skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.41,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can use that sound in a new song!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:07.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop destroying my fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.30,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yell on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.05,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm deleting this conversation \Nfrom my memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:15.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what overly strong love does to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Curvature of spacetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.47,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What are you seeing right now, Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:23.12,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get why she's so isolated at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.67,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,She's so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:25.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:30.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I wish everyone at her school \Ncould see how cool she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.86,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to talk to her \Nwhen school starts again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You totally should!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.55,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan's dream right now \Nis to drop out of school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.91,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Does that even count as a dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:45.62,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's use today to make a fun \Nsummer memory with Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.84,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a picture, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:52.20,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get some sea salt \Nsoft-serve. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:55.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No one said this was free time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.06,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san. Please wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:00.57,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.90,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.48,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You've really been out cold this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:15.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, Kita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,When was the last time I've been to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm here, \NI can see how beautiful it—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.49,Default,Beach Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:28.20,Default,Beach Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Come eat at our beach shack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.82,Default,Beach Man A,0000,0000,0000,,We got a discount for cuties like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:32.17,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a party animal in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.13,Default,Beach Man A,0000,0000,0000,,We can get you a table for four right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.38,Default,Beach Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Are y'all in high school? \NWhere'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.85,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Archetypal beach bros.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,They're too powerful for us to handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.01,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get away from the beach, ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.98,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H8A8881&\3c&HF9FCF5&\fay-0.15\pos(221.5,67.5)}Asahi Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.49,Default,Shopkeep,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.80,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Here, for you, Gotoh-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.65,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:04.20,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs10\c&HEDF0ED&\3c&H5D00BE&\bord1\pos(509,275)}Enoshima {\c&H5D00BE&\bord0}Fried\N {\fs12}Tako Senbei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:04.20,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\c&H5D00BE&\bord1.5\3c&HE6E9E6&\pos(476,296)}Asahi Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Takosen!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.52,0:12:04.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they press the takoyaki \Nwith a full ton of force!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A ton of force?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.58,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.03,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,My tastiness sensor never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.70,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,V-Very impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:19.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, I'm just glad \Nto see you feeling better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.20,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big and cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.17,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So photogenic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.97,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Here comes the selfie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:29.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:31.77,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It turned out super great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.81,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I ate tako senbei with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Summer memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.15,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.38,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's been wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,How are we at the climax already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:53.07,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And so, my summer came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.35,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We're just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.22,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,477)\shad2\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H9B998D&\3c&H5B553F&\4c&H202019&\pos(449,38)}Enoshima Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:10.97,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's climb all the way to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.14,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad2\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&HB9C5C3&\3c&H56605E&\4c&H3F4B49&\pos(366.5,34)}Enoshima Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.14,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:18.27,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything more beautiful \Nthan scenery you have to work to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.73,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,No. Screw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.12,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:21.88,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.01,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.29,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll{\i0} come with me, right, Ijichi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not super into it either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan! She's glowing more than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.04,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,H-How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.83,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,P-Perhaps her usually \Nunderstated extrovert aura
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.07,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,h-has been amplified \Nby the light of the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.21,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's stripped off her limiter, you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.38,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.38,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(855,1)\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\c&HD0B3FD&\pos(350,51.5)\3c&HD0B3FD&\bord4\fscx10\t(21,855,\fscx100)}Kit-aura
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.38,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(855,1)\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\c&H90F7F6&\pos(350,51.5)\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\fscx10\t(21,855,\fscx100)}K{\c&HC0C8FA&}i{\c&HF47FF2&}t{\c&HFFFFFF&}-{\c&HF0BBF3&}a{\c&HF585EF&}u{\c&HB9CCF9&}r{\c&HA5F5FA&}a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.21,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done. No more climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:55.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan's getting further \Nand further ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.48,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.45,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about the view?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:05.82,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.66,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We've only just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:16.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme take a break first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.15,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You've got so much energy, Kita-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:26.76,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Escar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:30.51,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I th-think we can ride an escalator up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.47,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's climb the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.85,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF6FEC7&\an7\fs8\3c&HAFB066&\bord1\pos(354,72)}Money Added: \NPurchase Price: \NChange:
