Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.85,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\bord2\an7\c&H69569C&\3c&HE2FE87&\pos(326,257)}B (Minor) \NEscar Full Trip \NElementary Student
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.85,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It costs money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:40.23,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You need to buy tickets \Nto the Enoshima Escar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:43.61,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,See, we should climb the stairs instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:45.61,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.68,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I... I have no money, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:52.80,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some pretty good bass guitars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.27,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.47,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.60,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,How about two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.18,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You want three?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:01.07,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You need to buy a ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:03.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:07.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But climbing the stairs would have \Nmade the view so much more impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:10.62,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You'll pay me back next month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.78,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I've never broken a promise in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.19,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't pay me back last time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it out of her paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:22.27,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're inhuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:28.20,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're here, \Nlet's hit up the observation deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Even taking the Escar is kind of exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.76,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It was... quite a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:40.21,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But being up this high \Nfeels quite liberating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.70,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,P-Positivity wells up within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.86,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That's the fresh air and \Nmagnificent view at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:48.55,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Should we take a picture together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.76,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,They're finally getting into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:56.70,Default,Miitan,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Isn't it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:57.93,Default,Takkun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.68,Default,Miitan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Aren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:05.48,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,141)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H4F5F51&\pos(259,289.5)\fs18}Tropical Love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:05.48,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,141)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H8673C7&\pos(448.5,294.5)\fs18}Tropical Love
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.14,Default,Takkun,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.95,Default,Takkun,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so pretty \NI forgot everything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.69,Default,Miitan,0000,0000,0000,,You silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:07.45,DefaultTop,Miitan,0000,0000,0000,,Miitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.13,DefaultTop,Miitan,0000,0000,0000,,Takkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.09,DefaultTop,Miitan,0000,0000,0000,,Miitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.65,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The observation deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.10,DefaultTop,Miitan,0000,0000,0000,,Takkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the observation deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.29,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:20.67,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The view from the observation deck \Nis even more fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.71,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We've really got to drink it all in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.51,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I love air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.71,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Err, You guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:33.54,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago, humans attempted \Nto build a tower to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.09,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,to prove themselves equal to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:40.08,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,God, enraged, scrambled \Nthe languages of humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.23,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and cast their lands into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about the Tower of Babel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:48.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But humans failed to learn \Nand built another tall tower like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.08,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! The scenery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:53.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan got what she wanted, \Nso let's blow this joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.37,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite part was the air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.05,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You filthy indoor types!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo. Weren't you eating sea salt \Nsoft-serve earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.98,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I've always got room for ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:12.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please pay me back for the ice cream, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.55,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I think we've had plenty of fun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.01,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we need one more \Nmemorable event...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat shirasu-don, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.90,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,They were sold out at the place \Nwhere we had lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.05,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Too full.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Since when were you in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.57,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.93,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the kites?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:42.55,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,They like to steal human food, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Right as we were talking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.96,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, you want my ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:58.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,They're targeting Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.45,Default,Kite A,0000,0000,0000,,She looks weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.92,Default,Kite B,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:03.31,Default,Kite C,0000,0000,0000,,Teach her a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.01,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Even birds look down on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even{\i0} birds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:10.16,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.16,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Memorable event achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the kind of memorable I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't stay out too late, \Nso we really should head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:25.37,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi's in bad shape, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:29.43,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a shrine visit \Nbefore we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.92,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\an8\bord2\fnArial Black\c&HACB3BF&\3c&H34377B&}Enoshima Benzaiten
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:37.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,This shrine is dedicated to a goddess \Ncalled Myo-on Benzaiten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She's the goddess of music \Nand performing arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:44.83,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought we should come here \Nif we ever went to Enoshima together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:50.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to wish for \Nour band's future success!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.45,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:04.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you were wishing \Npretty hard back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:06.10,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It took forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.83,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What were you wishing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:11.67,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I was wishing and thanking her \Npretty hard too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:15.09,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,"Goddess, thanks for making \Nour concert a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.57,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that good fortune coming!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.09,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get back to practice tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:25.38,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we don't have \Na next concert scheduled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.14,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.59,FlashbackItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.92,FlashbackItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back time to the first day of summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.61,FlashbackItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything, just turn back time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.98,FlashbackItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Either that, or give me fame and fortune \Nso that I never go hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,...that I made a really vapid wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.86,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's about an hour from here \Nto Shimo-Kita, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.62,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, you'll change \Ntrains at Fujisawa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:51.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.72,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Wake me up at Shimo-Kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.79,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:02.79,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish we'd gotten to do \Nsome Kamakura sightseeing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:05.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and I wish we'd had dinner together, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Shirasu-don...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.28,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She really wanted to eat that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:14.27,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My first long trip in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That was lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:20.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I almost wish we could've \Nstayed out a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.40,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.63,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's spend all of winter break \Nhanging out as Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.29,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you want to go, Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make memories together \Nevery single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:32.59,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I d-don't wanna go outside every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll th-think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.33,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.09,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You can rest if you want, Gotoh-san. \NI'll wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:43.15,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, I spent the whole \Ntrain ride up here unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.88,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm pretty alert now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.08,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.86,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Then the fun continues until Fujisawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.97,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Kita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:21:01.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I e-enjoyed hanging out with you all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I th-think I can face school\Nstarting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.16,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.18,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy the new term together, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:13.87,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:19.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This memory of summer will fuel me \Nthrough to winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.43,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan! It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.29,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.23,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're still in bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:31.39,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be late to school your first day back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:36.52,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel good. Wanna stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:40.14,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hitori-chan. Lying again\Njust to get out of school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:41.75,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.97,DefaultTop,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out, Futari!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:45.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-My muscles are so sore,\NI can't even move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:45.02,DefaultTop,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:50.33,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.33,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:57.94,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.00,Default,Kita's Friend A,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.00,0:22:02.72,Default,Kita's Friend A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kita-chan, I saw your \NIssta photos of Enoshima!
